<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Style Of Art</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        ul.list-group {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        table {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        h3, h4 {
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Back</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h3>Here is a comparison between term and artist_id The relationship between is counted</h3>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Term List</h4>
                <p><strong>The number of terms in the current database is {{ term_num }}</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    {% for item in term_list %}
                        <li class="list-group-item">{{ item[0] }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h4>Artist Tags</h4>
                <p><strong>Here is the ID of the top 10 artists with the most tags</strong></p>
                <table class="table table-striped">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Artist</th>
                            <th>Number</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for item in term_artist %}
                            <tr>
                                <td>{{ item[0] }}</td>
                                <td>{{ item[1] }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <p><strong>Here are the top 10 most frequent occurrences of term tags in the database and their occurrences</strong></p>
                <table class="table table-striped">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Term</th>
                            <th>Number</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for item in term_top %}
                            <tr>
                                <td>{{ item[0] }}</td>
                                <td>{{ item[1] }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
